  "text": [
    "The loneliest days,",
    "damp and indistinct,",
    "sea and land a haze.",
    "And purple fog horns",
    "blossomed over tides\u2014",
    "bruises being born",
    "in silence, so slow,",
    "so out there, around,",
    "above and below.",
    "In such hurts of sound",
    "the known world became",
    "neither flat nor round.",
    "The steaming tea pot",
    "was all we fathomed",
    "of",
    "and",
    ".",
    "The hours were hallways",
    "with doors at the ends",
    "opened into days",
    "fading into night",
    "and the scattering",
    "particles of light.",
    "Nothing was done then.",
    "Nothing was ever",
    "done. Then it was done."
  ],
  "title": "Fog Horns",
  "year": ""
}